OpenBand — Licensing
=====================

This repository contains **documentation, whitepaper, and protocol
specifications** for the OpenBand project. The **source code** for the
OpenBand mobile apps, gateway software, and exit-server configuration
is NOT in this repository and is not currently published.

Two separate licenses apply. Read carefully.


